               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360919-name-1159" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18360919-name-1159" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360919-name-1159" type="surname" value="DANBY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360919-name-1159" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE DANBY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am servant to Mr. Harry Izod, of Blackman-street On Wednesday, the 14th of September, I saw the prisoner there—he took the bacon and ran away with it—I ran, and overtook him in the Borough—I asked him where the bacon was—he said he knew nothing of it—I took him back to the shop—he fell on his knees, and confessed it—he said he was very poor.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> What did I do after I stole the bacon? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> You ran away—I saw you take it off a cheese—I do not know what you did with it—you had not got it when I took you—you came out of an alley.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360919-name-1160" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18360919-name-1160" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360919-name-1160" type="surname" value="MORRIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360919-name-1160" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN MORRIS</persName>
                  </hi>. On the 14th of September I saw the prisoner, between four and five o'clock, being pursued by Danby—I saw him turn the corner, and I picked the bacon up about twenty yards behind him—I did not see it in his possession, but I picked it up in the direction he was running.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I know nothing about it—I had not the bacon—I am a pensioner, and had just come up from Greenwich.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Guilty.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(The indictment also charged him with previous conviction.)</p>
